<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Happy Onam, Gaythri üå∏</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff8e7, #fceabb);
      overflow: hidden;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .message {
      position: absolute;
      top: 40%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4b2e05;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeIn 3s forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    .petal {
      position: absolute;
      top: -50px;
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      background-image: url('https://i.ibb.co/1zQvMHB/flower.png');
      background-size: cover;
      animation: fall linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes fall {
      0% { transform: translateY(-50px) rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: translateY(110vh) rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .boat {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 30px;
      left: -300px;
      width: 250px;
      animation: sail 20s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes sail {
      0% { left: -300px; }
      100% { left: 110%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Messages -->
  <div class="message" style="animation-delay: 0s">üå∏ Happy Onam, Ente Priye üå∏</div>
  <div class="message" style="animation-delay: 4s">Onam ke rangon jaise, teri zindagi hamesha khilti rahe,<br>Payasam ki mithaas jaise, tera dil hamesha meetha rahe.</div>
  <div class="message" style="animation-delay: 9s">Phoolon ke pookalam mein jaise khushbu basa karti hai,<br>Waise hi tu meri har dua mein hamesha basa karti hai.</div>
  <div class="message" style="animation-delay: 14s">Chahe jitni bhi doori ho iss Onam pe,<br>Mera pyaar hamesha tere paas hoga.</div>
  <div class="message" style="animation-delay: 19s">With all my love,<br>Yours forever, Akshat ‚ù§Ô∏è</div>

  <!-- Boat -->
  <img src="https://i.ibb.co/VWJw2cT/boat.png" alt="Boat" class="boat">

  <script>
    // Create falling petals
    function createPetal() {
      const petal = document.createElement('div');
      petal.classList.add('petal');
      petal.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
      petal.style.animationDuration = (5 + Math.random() * 5) + 's';
      document.body.appendChild(petal);
      setTimeout(() => petal.remove(), 10000);
    }

    setInterval(createPetal, 300);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
